{"tid":1980542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"灣仔警總接冒煙包裹　收件人為警務處處長鄧炳強","createTime":"2020-04-20T07:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T00:20:21.000Z","uid":20933,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"466b3b2295acb9620c03248e06128381d3671314","tid":1980542,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:08:38.000Z","msg":"灣仔警察總部接獲懷疑危險物品包裹。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，今日灣仔警署收到一個包裹，有職員拆開時包裹內有電池，並且出現煙冒，而信件收件人則為警務處處長鄧炳強。爆炸品處理課接報到場處理。"},{"pid":"a9d1e582141f05639051d580f3d6b932226b8c0b","tid":1980542,"uid":71624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:09:25.000Z","msg":"強仔屎忽有冇事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0c6cb92a3258f692a8e711537d508a641f31ad","tid":1980542,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"897b2ee1147248be0be57e2f82e361eb26cde881","tid":1980542,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:10:06.000Z","msg":"收件人邊會寫鄧炳強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ec9ab67eea1cdd7bab3757c9c2be753ff849a5","tid":1980542,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:10:57.000Z","msg":"冒煙都未爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e5c5f836c417b47d68bdf5c7f8f82fc4fe7453","tid":1980542,"uid":32816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"如獲至寶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6428cbdcc088a1579edf1ddc6d7f8fd8290f76","tid":1980542,"uid":334796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"自編自導自演"},{"pid":"eac10718457e502fc321c534b725b244955c0560","tid":1980542,"uid":293472,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"又寫劇本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34abe953fec1710ad23f2837f69ad86618dae4ed","tid":1980542,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:15:07.000Z","msg":"季炳強真係好鐘意出現"},{"pid":"9f310ff106971dcdac58a04f781b2e3947a7320c","tid":1980542,"uid":236878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf6ced9b85ce1c4815d6e6de567c162564f38f6","tid":1980542,"uid":310446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"叫咗你唔好淘寶買電池<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef52057a9a7bba6a85d569dd7426f8398ce7075","tid":1980542,"uid":20174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:37:24.000Z","msg":"原來係我朋友幫PK 頂咗，佢開咗個包裹燙傷左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2902c6fb51ad0b3c61af4735b0eb5e377a39d3d3","tid":1980542,"uid":193100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T22:42:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_97.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongpost.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout_us%2Fwhats_new%2Fnotices%2Findex_id_97.html&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPjC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=e5e4012f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongpost.hk/tc/about_us/whats_new/notices/index_id_97.html</a><br />\n禁止郵寄鋰電池<br />\n2015.10.05<br />\n為確保郵件在運送途中不會構成危險，違禁品或危險品均不得郵寄（包括空郵和平郵）。<br />\n<br />\n根據國際郵政規例，鋰電池屬危險品之一，嚴禁經郵遞途徑寄運。香港郵政為加強郵政保安，確保郵件在運送途中不會構成危險，由二○一五年十月十九日起鋰電池的禁運限制將擴展至平郵郵件。<br />\n<br />\n寄件人嚴禁以任何郵遞服務或寄運方式投寄鋰電池。在郵件處理的過程中如發現鋰電池，有關物品會被退回，而寄件人不會獲退還郵費，更有可能被檢控。有關禁寄物品、報關表格和海外目的地投寄要求的詳情分別載於《郵政指南》第6.3 段、第9.5 段和附錄。"},{"pid":"5fe8d787c9cfbb7a0ad05828cc0b21fff20e90de","tid":1980542,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T23:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EKhigXRUYAEoBZj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEKhigXRUYAEoBZj.jpg&h=0a771d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據過往案例 郵包寫邊個名就係果個人擁有 咁今次個炸彈嘅擁有人係邊個已經呼之欲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cf641e9e575eaa5d6657fd9a973eb75b2aa029","tid":1980542,"uid":13428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe8d787c9cfbb7a0ad05828cc0b21fff20e90de","tid":1980542,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T23:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EKhigXRUYAEoBZj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEKhigXRUYAEoBZj.jpg&h=0a771d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據過往案例 郵包寫邊個名就係果個人擁有 咁今次個炸彈嘅擁有人係邊個已經呼之欲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T23:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c8dadaa04fb2b7c3ade4262d939805b5d828c4","tid":1980542,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19cf641e9e575eaa5d6657fd9a973eb75b2aa029","tid":1980542,"uid":13428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe8d787c9cfbb7a0ad05828cc0b21fff20e90de","tid":1980542,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T23:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EKhigXRUYAEoBZj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEKhigXRUYAEoBZj.jpg&h=0a771d97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據過往案例 郵包寫邊個名就係果個人擁有 咁今次個炸彈嘅擁有人係邊個已經呼之欲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTim